Planner note

This packet is intentionally not a docs-beautification packet.
Its purpose is to create the evidence substrate the docs have been missing.

Canonical evidence should come from the manifest-driven suite.
Real-world intuition and practical shape should come from live corpus runs.
Both are valuable; they are not the same thing.
